                        <div class="highlighted panel-content__highlighted">
                            <p>Which currency gets processed at checkout?  The currency that payments are actually processed in will always be the default currency. If checkout is set to Optimized One-Page Checkout, the shopper will see their chosen display currency as well as which currency they will actually be charged. Other checkouts and all invoice emails will display the prices in the store's default currency.</p>
